c1->SetWindowSize(1200,400);
c1->Clear();
c1->Divide(3,1);
TCut cut = "x1hit==2 && y1hit==2";
tree->SetAlias("x0a","x1e[0]");
tree->SetAlias("x1a","x1e[1]");
tree->SetAlias("y0a","y1e[0]");
tree->SetAlias("y1a","y1e[1]");
